CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1946, pg. 28 reads: "Kiddies Celebrate - Adorable little Ann B. Cromartie, daughter of Pvt. and Mrs. Howard Cromartie, celebrated her first birthday at the home of her aunt, Mrs. Eula Jessup, of Wylie Avenue, last week. Guests were Elmer Jessup Jr., Leathia Blacks, Mayland Bryant, Shirley Lockett, and Furman Meggett Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Children, including Elmer Jessup Jr., Leathia Blacks, Mayland Bryant, Shirley Lockett, and Furman Meggett Jr., surrounding Ann B. Cromartie, standing behind her birthday cake with single large candle, in home of Eula Jessup, Wylie Avenue, Hill District
